    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i'll call the clinic in the morning but he's really uncomfortable right now and it's late. i just want to know if aspirin is actually safe to use for an 8 year old in the meantime? i've seen it help for adults so i'm wondering if it works the same way for kids too.",
